name: Covid19 Coin
description:
The emergence of COVID19 coin Token is to help all mankind fight the virus and provide a quality life experience.
COVID19 coin Token gives its users the opportunity to automatically help all mankind every time they transfer money.
7% of each transaction will go to the charity wallet, Each month the money will be used for masks, ventilators, disinfectants, medicines and food to charities around the world.
